data.description: Amazing remodeled house in the 55+ Clearbrook community. What you get is a beautiful club house, 2 pools, lawn maintenance, roof repairs, snow cleaning just to name a few great things this community has to offer. very peaceful and quiet back yard overlooking the golf course which is also located in this community. Spacious master bedroom with master bath, two car garage, newly remodeled kitchen. too many great things to list, must come and see to appreciate all the love that was put into this house. Feel free to call with any questions 646-932-0428. Offering 2% buyer's agent fee
